org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN issue_statuses ON issue_statuses.id = issues.status_id INNER JOIN trackers ON trackers.id = issues.tracker_id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN enumerations ON enumerations.id = issues.priority_id AND enumerations.type IN ('IssuePriority') WHERE (SELECT 1 FROM journals WHERE journals.journalized_type = 'Issue' AND journals.journalized_id = issues.id AND journals.user_id IN ('69') AND (journals.private_notes = False OR journals.user_id = 69 OR 1 = 0)) IS NOT NULL
